  "title": "n8n API: Create credential",
  "body": "curl -X POST \"{{n8n-url}}/api/v1/credentials\" \\\n  -H \"X-N8N-API-KEY: {{api-key}}\" \\\n  -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" \\\n  -d '{\n    \"name\": \"{{credential-name}}\",\n    \"type\": \"{{credential-type}}\",\n    \"data\": {}\n  }'",
  "description": "Create new credential programmatically - automate credential setup (docs.n8n.io/api/api-reference/)",
